To build and install lgmon:

        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --enable-progpath=/usr/bin --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        make
        make install

To build and install lgmon with AUTOCONF

You can set the following <Printer Model Name>.
            e500
            mg2100
            mg3100
            mg4100
            mg5300
            mg6200
            mg8200
            ip4900

Example for building the mg6200 lgmon with the new automake and autoconf:
        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=mg6200
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --enable-progpath=/usr/bin --program-suffix=mg6200
        make
        make install

